torque is in foot-pounds. The constant 7127 is used when torque is in Newto=
n-meters.</span></p><ul><li aria-level=3D"1"><h3>Explanation of the Math</h=
3></li></ul><h4><i>For Torque in lb-ft:</i></h4><p><span style=3D"font-weig=
ht: 400;">We know that, for torque in lb-ft, the formula of horsepower is:<=
